nodes.bodyText:
Instead of the onOrAfter checks, I would prefer a method on SnapshotsService of the form
boolean useShardGenerations(Version repositoryMetaVersion) {
  return repositoryMetaVersion.onOrAfter(Version.V_7_6_0);
}

and then remove the public SHARD_GEN_IN_REPO_DATA_VERSION field.

